column1: TAI Time at Start of Scan replicated across the swath (Time UTC+0)
column4: Deep Blue AOT at 0.55 micron for land with higher quality data (Quality flag=2,3) (None)
column5: Standard deviation of Deep Blue AOT at 0.55 micron for land with  all quality data (Quality flag=1,2,3) (None)
column6: Deep Blue Aerosol Confidence Flag (0= No Confidence (or fill),  1= Marginal, 2= Good, 3= Very Good) (None)
column7: Averaged topographic altitude (in km) for Land (KM)
